## Description

The breadcrumb trail tag is used for displaying the hierarchy of the current page. It can be fully
customized by changing its used options (see [configuration option reference]({relocatable:
../reference_configuration.html}) for detailed information on the options):

* `tag.breadcrumbtrail.separator`
* `tag.breadcrumbtrail.omit_last`
* `tag.breadcrumbtrail.omit_index_path`

The behavior of the `tag.breadcrumbtrail.omit_index_path` option can be overridden for individual
index paths by setting the meta information `omit_index_path` accordingly.

